				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You must be able to generate new sound data each frame, rather than generating it all in advance. Start by generating a little more than 1/60 second worth of samples every frame. This will slowly fill the host's sound buffer, eventually causing your alBufferData() to block a few milliseconds, unless this "al" driver is broken.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

